{"name":"Accurate Attack","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>When you make an accurate attack, you can take a penalty of up to –5 on the effect modifier of the attack and add the same number (up to +5) to your attack bonus.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"p0zfe86es1"}
{"name":"Agile Feint","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You can use your Acrobatics bonus or movement speed rank in place of Deception to feint and trick in combat.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"sobz5hk80gb"}
{"name":"All-out Attack","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>When you make an all-out attack, you can take a penalty of up to –5 on your active defenses (Dodge and Parry) and add the same number (up to +5) to your attack bonus.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"ql734806gl7"}
{"name":"Animal Empathy","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You have a special connection with animals. You can use interaction skills on animals normally, and do not have to speak a language the animal understands.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"rbyl83318u"}
{"name":"Artificer","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You can use the Expertise: Magic skill to create temporary magical devices.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"2qxnwg01u2u"}
{"name":"Assessment","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You can use Insight to able to judge an opponent’s relative combat capabilities.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"bj7emcsorzm"}
{"name":"Attractive","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You are particularly attractive, giving you a +2 circumstance bonus on Deception and Persuasion checks to deceive, mislead, or influence others who are attracted to you. Rank 2 gives a +5 bonus.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"u4dkdsbdhoa"}
{"name":"Beginner's Luck","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>By spending a hero point, you gain an effective 5 ranks in a skill in which you currently have 0 ranks.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"xcj54swu19"}
{"name":"Benefit","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You have some significant social or structural benefit, such as wealth, status, or a secret identity. Each rank provides one benefit.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"5m5pq21lnfm"}
{"name":"Chokehold","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>If you successfully grab and maintain a hold on an opponent, you can suffocate them.</p>","equipement":false,"rang":1,"edit":true,"listEffectsVariantes":{}},"effects":[],"_id":"c9o9j3zq7bq"}